Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.22,0:00:18.15,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算翻過所有的雜誌也沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.51,0:00:22.11,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在這搖頭嘆息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.39,0:00:26.50,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本找不到 與我相稱的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.63,0:00:30.54,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世紀末的流行色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.86,0:00:34.58,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都無法 討得你的歡心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.78,0:00:38.38,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉讓你失望了 對不起啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.54,0:00:43.17,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰這樣不穩的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.71,0:00:47.34,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖晃晃的又有什麼不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.50,0:00:51.35,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此還是得向前邁進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.74,0:00:56.02,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說  一點也不成問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.97,0:01:05.07,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是與我緊緊地纏繞的話不行喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.16,0:01:08.87,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你  別用那種冷冷的眼神望著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.06,0:01:12.71,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我照著自己的步調去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.07,0:01:16.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話我很快就會崩潰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.41,0:01:20.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如履薄冰這樣不穩的步伐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.44,0:01:24.88,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖晃晃的又有什麼不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.33,0:01:29.41,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此還是得向前邁進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.72,0:01:34.06,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說  一點也不成問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.78,0:22:14.80,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  真正的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.29,0:22:20.46,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  這就是愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.71,0:22:25.88,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冰冷的黑暗中  伸手尋找溫暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.01,0:22:31.71,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天  奇蹟也一定會發生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.30,0:22:44.67,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 如果有愛 就絕對有具體的形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.19,0:22:55.70,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic 現在 在我手中 有誕生的氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.95,0:23:03.96,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是精神飽滿  也不能   太過勉強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.34,0:23:09.21,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  把些微的勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.70,0:23:20.41,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Free Magic  凝聚起來  培育茁壯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.60,0:00:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瞬間明白所有真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.40,0:00:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要開始就無法停止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.21,0:00:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天偵探團外宿集訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.90,0:00:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美和元太竟然消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.90,0:00:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.50,0:00:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.21,0:00:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.29,0:00:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.50,0:01:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年偵探團消失事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.42,0:01:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連續度假屋怪人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.69,0:01:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人和管理員被殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.83,0:01:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世間真是太可怕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.93,0:01:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過呢 不需要大腦的強盜事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.70,0:01:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不需要名偵探出場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.12,0:02:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.76,0:02:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 柯南那傢伙呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.90,0:02:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在睡覺嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.13,0:02:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.67,0:02:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南他去外宿集訓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.32,0:02:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市內的兒童會舉辦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.02,0:02:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.46,0:02:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次兒童會要演布偶劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.78,0:02:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布偶劇？ 集訓？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.85,0:02:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到霧丘高原的度假屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.28,0:02:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的小孩子都會一起在那過夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.30,0:02:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那些小鬼偵探團也在一起嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.09,0:02:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知道會不會有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.71,0:02:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.52,0:02:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是報紙上寫的那個度假屋怪人啊 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.10,0:02:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.90,0:02:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地方完全不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.80,0:02:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過霧丘高原一到晚上之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.49,0:02:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個山區都會被濃霧給籠罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.61,0:02:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不小心迷路的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.48,0:03:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該有大人陪同吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.21,0:03:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是三丁目的海部先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.82,0:03:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說他當學生的時候曾演過布偶劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.24,0:03:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這次的兒童會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.10,0:03:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就請他幫忙寫劇本和指導
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.96,0:03:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.90,0:03:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.13,0:03:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了 又少了一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.37,0:03:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.68,0:03:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太 你根本沒有投入感情去念台詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.95,0:03:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.44,0:03:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太 再來一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.54,0:03:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了 又少了一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.90,0:03:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.19,0:03:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.70,0:03:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是什麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.03,0:03:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 光彥那小子神氣什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.51,0:03:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.94,0:03:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.66,0:03:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人犯一定就在這裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.81,0:03:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中生還玩布偶啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.35,0:04:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就不來了 和灰原一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.00,0:04:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對那種東西沒興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.85,0:04:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.00,0:04:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人羡慕的角色啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 這樣不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.72,0:04:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是偵探角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.51,0:04:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多一些威嚴和震撼力才行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.51,0:04:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 海部老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.77,0:04:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別叫我老師嘛 光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.43,0:04:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是第一次負責演出的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.06,0:04:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是柯南的角色應該…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.61,0:04:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說得沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.79,0:04:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你再試一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.79,0:04:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人犯一定就在這裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.94,0:04:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布偶的動作還是差一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.43,0:04:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彥到底在興奮什麼嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.37,0:04:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說那個海部先生剛剛搬來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.22,0:04:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和光彥作了好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.69,0:04:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這次的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.04,0:04:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是自己說要幫忙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.48,0:05:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我記得這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.25,0:05:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂然後所有人都消失了＂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.52,0:05:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是＂懸疑女王＂阿嘉莎•克莉斯汀的名作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.00,0:05:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.45,0:05:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.45,0:05:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被困在某座島上的人 一個一個都被殺了的故事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.75,0:05:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰的都無所謂 我肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.15,0:05:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.31,0:05:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 就到此為止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.52,0:05:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一小時之後吃完飯再繼續吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.14,0:05:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布偶不要弄丟了 要把它放好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.75,0:05:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.39,0:05:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飯了吃飯了 鰻魚飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.91,0:05:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.44,0:05:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.11,0:05:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.11,0:05:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借過一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.52,0:05:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大家還不夠熟練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.80,0:05:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要特訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.31,0:05:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特訓 做特訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.70,0:06:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.19,0:06:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃飯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.21,0:06:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好濃的霧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.90,0:06:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是霧丘高原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.86,0:06:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃得好飽 動都不想動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.22,0:06:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 休息30分鐘 然後繼續練習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.27,0:06:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要繼續練習？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.38,0:06:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彥 饒了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.30,0:06:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太 我還準備了宵夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.57,0:06:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我願意繼續練習 快點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.00,0:06:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.56,0:06:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有看到老師？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.85,0:06:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.39,0:06:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.23,0:06:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然不見他的蹤影了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.70,0:06:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練習的時間到了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.77,0:06:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽你這麼一說 三丁目的小朋友好像都不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.46,0:06:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶 他們到哪裡去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.73,0:06:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們有沒有看見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.13,0:07:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.89,0:07:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布偶也不見了 三丁目小孩們的布偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.92,0:07:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶 老師的也不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.74,0:07:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根本就像…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.98,0:07:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定三丁目那些人拿走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.73,0:07:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他們去哪裡了呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.26,0:07:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛...可能是回家去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.40,0:07:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種時間回家？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.95,0:07:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種濃霧下啊..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.46,0:07:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外…外面好像有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.73,0:07:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.01,0:07:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧太濃 什麼也看不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.87,0:07:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定不會錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.44,0:07:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才這裡的確有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.83,0:07:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 連他們也不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.77,0:08:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.23,0:08:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布…布偶也不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.44,0:08:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下我們四個人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.37,0:08:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 這玩笑也開得太大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.12,0:08:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和「然後所有人都消失了」完全一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.90,0:08:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這麼說 這次要演出的布偶劇現在變成真的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.09,0:08:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在原作裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.34,0:08:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當殺了一個人之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.13,0:08:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布偶就會消失一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.71,0:08:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺…殺了一個之後…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.38,0:08:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要亂說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.85,0:08:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼消失的小朋友 他們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.68,0:08:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.95,0:08:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜 事情還不能斷定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.76,0:08:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.21,0:09:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也是濃霧一片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.24,0:09:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳印 是那些小孩子的腳印吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.86,0:09:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個大人的腳印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.00,0:09:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.46,0:09:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是剛才站在窗戶旁邊的那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.16,0:09:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.33,0:09:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的腳印的大小和這裡的完全不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.40,0:09:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.35,0:09:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天這些度假屋租出去的只有這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.21,0:09:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理員是這樣說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.69,0:09:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.48,0:09:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.72,0:09:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我可以確定在這度假區發生了什麼事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.46,0:09:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點不會錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.75,0:09:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.81,0:09:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.49,0:09:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.68,0:09:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是那個所謂的度假屋怪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.28,0:09:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的度假屋怪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.74,0:09:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是電視新聞講的那個嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.45,0:09:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.25,0:09:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.84,0:09:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他將大家關在某處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.59,0:09:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後趁機搶劫這度假區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.25,0:10:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原…原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.40,0:10:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 就讓我們少年偵探團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.98,0:10:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那度假屋怪人給抓出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.21,0:10:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.78,0:10:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年偵探團又要出動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.85,0:10:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這主意不錯 開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.52,0:10:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.20,0:10:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.16,0:10:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就算是度假屋怪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶走小孩還可以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.68,0:10:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼連布偶也一起帶走呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.18,0:10:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全搞不懂 真煩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.20,0:10:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是先去報警吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.52,0:10:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年偵探團要開始先調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.40,0:10:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在警察來之後也不遲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.31,0:10:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.87,0:10:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.53,0:10:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不通嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.60,0:10:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點聲音也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.94,0:10:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來 我們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.69,0:11:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經完全被困在濃霧裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.00,0:11:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.40,0:11:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到別的管理處去應該會有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.73,0:11:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要到那裡去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.70,0:11:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.13,0:11:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡應該有手電筒和蠟燭吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.22,0:11:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這裡的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.43,0:11:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做確認的時候檢查過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.30,0:11:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.73,0:11:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能被人拿走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.55,0:11:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人拿走 被誰拿走呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.77,0:11:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.15,0:11:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是度假屋怪人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.87,0:11:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 現在還不能斷定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.75,0:11:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣就算要到附近的度假屋也很容易迷路的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.72,0:11:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我們先在這屋裡尋找線索吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.65,0:11:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然希望不大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.41,0:11:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.03,0:12:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美 妳和元太留在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.80,0:12:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿他沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.39,0:12:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太 步美就交給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.72,0:12:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.42,0:12:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心啊 柯南 光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.90,0:12:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.33,0:12:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.48,0:12:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是海部先生跟其他小朋友的房間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.86,0:12:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們進去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.71,0:12:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.71,0:12:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這附近的地圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.22,0:12:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中有幾個度假屋還劃上了記號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.09,0:12:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底意味著什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.59,0:12:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.19,0:12:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.49,0:13:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.89,0:13:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海部老師是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.49,0:13:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.83,0:13:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.11,0:13:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太 步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.88,0:13:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.72,0:13:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.38,0:13:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 柯南…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.79,0:13:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.50,0:13:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只剩下我們兩個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.01,0:13:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.79,0:13:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是老師他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.93,0:13:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海部老師他就是度假屋怪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.83,0:13:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那張地圖和工具箱就是決定性的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.44,0:13:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種濃霧下的度假屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.00,0:13:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最適合的就是這布偶劇的劇本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.96,0:13:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然連我們也欺騙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.27,0:13:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.59,0:13:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.78,0:13:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止小孩 連布偶也一起不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.12,0:14:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這不像是度假屋怪人的手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.10,0:14:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想太多了 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.39,0:14:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,況且能夠拿走布偶的只有老師一個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.87,0:14:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.78,0:14:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我們先去找元太和步美吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.75,0:14:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.34,0:14:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再把犯人給抓出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.94,0:14:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我們的雙手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.42,0:14:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得隔壁的度假屋是往這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.94,0:14:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.27,0:14:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是隔壁的度假屋的話 怎麼那麼近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.77,0:14:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我們過去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.83,0:14:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.36,0:14:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.41,0:15:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海部…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.51,0:15:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.01,0:15:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果…果然是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.19,0:15:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿咧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.44,0:15:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.94,0:15:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們快點進去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.08,0:15:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.30,0:15:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.28,0:15:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去二樓看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.26,0:15:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你留在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.54,0:15:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點回來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.64,0:15:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.94,0:15:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.44,0:16:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.29,0:16:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.03,0:16:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.84,0:16:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.76,0:16:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.35,0:16:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彥 快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.21,0:16:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 柯南…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.27,0:16:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然連柯南也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.45,0:16:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.77,0:16:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只剩下你一個了 光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.14,0:16:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.95,0:16:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.00,0:16:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來人啊 來人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.02,0:17:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.68,0:17:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼逃都沒用的 光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.12,0:17:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我走吧 光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.65,0:17:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來 不要過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.83,0:17:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別不聽話嘛 光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.03,0:17:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.52,0:17:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.28,0:17:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.76,0:17:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.91,0:18:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.35,0:18:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南…還有大家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.90,0:18:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.54,0:18:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.72,0:18:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我是在替大家做特訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.30,0:18:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要他們一個一個來其他的度假屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.64,0:18:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以這樣 我完全不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.32,0:18:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我忘記告訴你們四個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.06,0:18:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼老師屋裏的工具怎麼解釋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.13,0:18:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想做一些簡單的舞台道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.43,0:18:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家能早點進入自己扮演的角色的狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.29,0:18:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那張地圖呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.06,0:18:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是為了怕迷路而準備的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.94,0:18:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我聽說這附近的霧很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.39,0:18:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.04,0:18:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失的布偶也是為了特訓而拿走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.79,0:19:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彥 你很怕吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.20,0:19:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.71,0:19:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元太你自己不是也怕得要命嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.05,0:19:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪有？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.99,0:19:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那時候大家在做發聲練習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.45,0:19:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然看起來像是被綁架了一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.67,0:19:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我真的是這樣看到的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.95,0:19:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.63,0:19:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.33,0:19:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後連我也參了一腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.35,0:19:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實那個時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.15,0:19:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彥 快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.16,0:19:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.80,0:19:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.51,0:19:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.71,0:19:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只剩下光彥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.25,0:19:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家繼續練習吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.46,0:19:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.77,0:19:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙今天神氣了一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.05,0:19:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們來嚇嚇他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.27,0:19:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做不太好吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.94,0:19:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這也許對練習會有幫助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.11,0:19:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些傢伙還真壞心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.62,0:19:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.57,0:19:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然連步美也這樣對我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.03,0:20:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.89,0:20:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海部老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.98,0:20:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要連電話線也切斷呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.03,0:20:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.54,0:20:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是老師嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.47,0:20:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.03,0:20:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是老師 那是誰做的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.98,0:20:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.32,0:20:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.40,0:20:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.28,0:20:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.37,0:20:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是真的度假屋怪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.37,0:20:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.45,0:20:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.57,0:20:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.69,0:20:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.06,0:20:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.69,0:20:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 還有大家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.82,0:20:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說切斷電話線 拿走手電筒的人難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.58,0:20:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.69,0:20:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.40,0:20:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的度假屋怪人幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.46,0:20:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.60,0:20:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.03,0:20:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會變成怎樣都沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.96,0:20:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家別管我 快把他給抓起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.10,0:20:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.19,0:21:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死人了 給我閉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.44,0:21:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.27,0:21:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這臭小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.91,0:21:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.52,0:21:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.55,0:21:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鈞一髮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.39,0:21:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.11,0:21:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.41,0:21:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你閉一下眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.45,0:21:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要閉上哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.42,0:21:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彥 剛才真對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.02,0:21:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你刮目相看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.39,0:21:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好幸福啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.97,0:21:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彥 你這傢伙 不可原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.50,0:21:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別吃醋啊 元太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.84,0:21:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛親的是哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.20,0:23:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天後市內舉辦了兒童會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.29,0:23:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的布偶劇也登場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.73,0:23:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果當然是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.56,0:23:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.51,0:23:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絡…絡繰嶺的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.99,0:23:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜘蛛公館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.43,0:23:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圖釘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.40,0:24:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然表面生銹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.56,0:24:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過針還是新的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.59,0:24:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過爸爸說過不可以出去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.06,0:24:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 快點起來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.67,0:24:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭有危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.80,0:24:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.03,0:24:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥取縣蜘蛛公館之怪事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.47,0:24:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.72,0:24:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚的數量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.47,0:24:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次在鳥取縣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.33,0:24:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平次將出場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.47,0:24:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥取平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.47,0:24:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部平次
